description: Decimal expansion of square root of 67.
comments: Continued fraction expansion is 8 followed by {5, 2, 1, 1, 7, 1, 1, 2, 5, 16} repeated. - _Harry J. Smith_, Jun 08 2009
links: Harry J. Smith, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..20000
prog: (PARI) { default(realprecision, 20080); x=sqrt(67); for (n=1, 20000, d=floor(x); x=(x-d)*10; write("b010519.txt", n, " ", d)); } \\ _Harry J. Smith_, Jun 08 2009
crossrefs: Cf. A010147 Continued fraction. - _Harry J. Smith_, Jun 08 2009
